00:00:02.909 --> 00:00:04.680
My name is Ahmad Bahye, I'm a data Analyst

00:00:04.680 --> 00:00:05.910
course manager at Udacity

00:00:05.910 --> 00:00:07.319
and I'd like to talk to you about

00:00:07.319 --> 00:00:09.030
one million arab coders' business analyst
program

00:00:09.030 --> 00:00:10.940
The aim of the program is to provide students

00:00:10.940 --> 00:00:13.330
with
the fundamental skills and expertise for analyzing

00:00:13.330 --> 00:00:14.330
data.

00:00:14.330 --> 00:00:15.959
Delving into more details, first the program

00:00:15.959 --> 00:00:18.570
starts by teaching
students necessary basics of statistics and

00:00:18.570 --> 00:00:19.940
programming

00:00:19.940 --> 00:00:22.880
Then the program focuses on improving the

00:00:22.880 --> 00:00:26.350
students' skills in
collecting and analyzing data and explaining

00:00:26.350 --> 00:00:27.350
the analysis results

00:00:27.350 --> 00:00:30.300
and how to present the results in a correct

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:33.070
and simple way to take part in decision making

00:00:33.070 --> 00:00:37.870
By the end of the program students should

00:00:37.870 --> 00:00:38.870
have the sufficient technical knowledge

00:00:38.870 --> 00:00:40.640
that qualifies them to start their journey

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:42.420
of
research and self-development to become data

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:43.420
analysts

00:00:43.420 --> 00:00:44.649
As for job opportunities, where there is data

00:00:44.649 --> 00:00:47.010
there's the
need to extract information needed for decision

00:00:47.010 --> 00:00:48.010
making

00:00:48.010 --> 00:00:50.430
And this is where the Data Analyst's role

00:00:50.430 --> 00:00:51.430
comes in

00:00:51.430 --> 00:00:52.430
with job opportunities present at data-centric

00:00:52.430 --> 00:00:53.430
corporations like Microsoft and Google

00:00:53.430 --> 00:00:58.500
in addition to jobs at companies and institutions

00:00:58.500 --> 00:01:04.970
in the fields of support and decision-making

00:01:04.970 --> 00:01:13.040
The aim of this program is to provide

00:01:13.040 --> 00:01:15.750
oppurtunnities with no prior conditions

00:01:15.750 --> 00:01:19.250
in order to educate the highest number of

00:01:19.250 --> 00:01:22.760
skilled data anaysts.
this matters because it helps develop each

00:01:22.760 --> 00:01:23.760
individual

00:01:23.760 --> 00:01:24.979
and his technological knowledge, enabling

00:01:24.979 --> 00:01:29.670
them to utilize
the available technology to serve the community

00:01:29.670 --> 00:01:30.940
and society

